Medium is 6-8

description:
This dress is an attention getter all by itself! This very stretchy dress comes in an all over leopard pattern with gold fringe chains and studded shoulder embellishments! Zip-Back.

Medium fits 6-8
Large fits 10-12

The first number indicates a nice fit, second number is a tighter fit.
